Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs25\bord1.5\c&H9E6FE6&\3c&H0E1225&\an7\b1\pos(251.867,632.668)}霸伊斯亞修
